"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据多方消息称，前国脚张恩华去世。昨天他刚刚度过 48 岁生日。 张恩华 1973 年出生，1996 年入选国家队，为米卢带领的国足征战 2002 年韩日世界杯成员，共代表国家队出场 59 次，进 5 球。在俱乐部方面，张恩华是大连实德队主力后卫，是大连夺得联赛「七冠王」的主要功臣之一。 北京时间 4 月 29 日，张恩华的离世震惊了中国足坛。据悉，张恩华在前一天的生日宴上喝了不少酒，但当时意识清醒，没有不适，之后又去朋友处继续庆祝。 但在回家后，张恩华出现了休克的情况，家人迅速叫了救护车。救护车到来后进行了心肺复苏等急救程序，转到医院后继续全力抢救，但最终无力回天。据朋友透露，张恩华不嗜酒，平日里也很少喝酒。前一天的饭局，一是庆祝自己的生日，而也是与自己的新团队吃饭团建。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-2b69e98adfe7e90fb0166b1b37a6ba92_200x0.gif"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "513 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/457170964"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4trnpuy8mdUIEAMaCDYzODczNjI2IOSOqoQGMAQ4hAFACXIJNDU3MTcwOTY0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1619709182.305517", "card_id": "Q_444218811", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1605}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "1+0.1+0.01+0.001+0.0001... 一直下去会在实际中到达 2 吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-7b4d66ec3f563d9b4f38bc9f2443d1bf_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "497 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/444218811"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI4trnpuy8mdUIEAMaCDYwOTkzODU3IM3SnYEGMOwBOKAYQApyCTQ0NDIxODgxMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1619709182.3059", "card_id": "Q_457178922", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 91}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "辽宁 102:98 加时险胜广东，大比分扳成 1:1，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-935edc8358897f40e74b48556d821fa4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "494 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/457178922"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4trnpuy